title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Dolpa Juphal Airport - version 1.4
description:
In this addon spotlight we are going to look at  Dolpa Juphal Airport (VNDP) version 1.4 which has been released a few days ago. This addon has been created by a community member and is one of the most dangerous airports in Nepal.

If you want to give the airport a try yourself you can download it from the site below: 
https://flightsim.to/file/1307/dolpha-juphal-airport-v1-0-vndp-nepal
